when is humanitarian intervention justified and is torture ever justified readings include charles beitz thomas pogge and john rawls stanford center for ethics in society search pgj news of interest kieran oberman tteching global justice class april 12 2011 news postdoctoral fellowships for program on global justice november 23 2010 announcement program on global justice center for ethics in society seek postdoctoral fellows for 2009 2010 october 30 2008 announcement fellowship in global justice january 18 2007 announcement support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 3241 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
